G4083.\par
}{\plain \fs20 \fs20 \par
}{\plain \fs20 \b\fs20 Dead}{\plain \fs20 \b\super\fs20 *}{\plain \fs20 \fs20  is a Greek word, G5053, literally translated as {\u8216\'91}ended{\u8217\'92} or {\u8216\'91}finished.{\u8217\'92}\par
