Testament.}{\plain \fs20 \b\fs20  Never read the Old Testament & New Testament together}{\plain \fs20 \fs20 , too confusing even for the mature \softline
Christian.}{\plain \fs20 \fs20 \par
}{\plain \fs20 \fs20 \par
