{\plain \fs20 \fs20 \line A. You* (plural) vs. You (singular). A lot of teachings are lost because there is no way to know who is being \softline
addressed, a crowd or an individual. \line B. The {\u8216\'91}Checks & balance system{\u8217\'92} of being an {\u8216\'91}Open Translation{\u8217\'92} with the possibility of over a million people \softline
watching has kept the MLV pure from denominational or theological slants. No one has ever submitted \softline
{\u8216\'91}indoctrinations{\u8217\'92} because they know the next person will just take them out. \par
}\pard \fs20\qj\tx0\tx1134\tx2268\tx3402\tx4536\tx5670\tx6804\tx7938\tx9072 
{\plain \fs20 \fs20 C. 12-13 year old reading level.\par
