}\pard \fs20\qj\tx0\tx1134\tx2268\tx3402\tx4536\tx5670\tx6804\tx7938\tx9072 
{\plain \fs20 \fs20 E. You have the ability to read the New Testament in chronological order; start in Mark and continue. \par
}\pard \fs20\qj\tx0\tx1134\tx2268\tx3402\tx4536\tx5670\tx6804\tx7938\tx9072 
